1
00:00:03,410 --> 00:00:06,384
我想出了一个科学笑话 你想听吗?
I've invented a science joke, would you like to hear it?

2
00:00:06,385 --> 00:00:07,564
当然
Sure.

3
00:00:07,565 --> 00:00:11,166
扭进一个灯泡需要多少个爱迪生?
How many Edisons does it take to screw in a light bulb?

4
00:00:11,168 --> 00:00:12,835
多少个?
How many?

5
00:00:12,837 --> 00:00:14,837
无所谓 灯泡的主意是他剽窃的
Who cares? He stole the idea

6
00:00:14,839 --> 00:00:17,172
所以他没资格有自己的笑话
and doesn't deserve his own joke.

7
00:00:17,174 --> 00:00:18,741
真的是剽窃的吗?
Is that really true?

8
00:00:18,743 --> 00:00:21,410
当然 这才算是好笑话
Of course, that's how you know it's a good joke.

9
00:00:21,412 --> 00:00:24,046
不仅有娱乐性 还能教人知识
It not only entertains, it informs.

10
00:00:25,515 --> 00:00:27,082
嘿 抱歉打扰了
Hey, sorry to interrupt.

11
00:00:27,084 --> 00:00:28,417
呃 Barry
Uh, Barry,

12
00:00:28,419 --> 00:00:31,620
扭进一个灯泡需要多少个爱迪生?
uh, how many Edisons does it take to screw in a light bulb?

13
00:00:31,622 --> 00:00:34,022
你知道其实爱迪生没有发明灯泡吧?
Did you know Edison didn't actually invent the light bulb?

14
00:00:37,260 --> 00:00:39,595
你来干嘛 Barry?
What do you want, Barry?

15
00:00:39,597 --> 00:00:42,598
只是想把这份小谢礼送给Amy
Just wanted to drop this off as a little thank you for Amy.

16
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,932
谢我什么?
What's this for?

17
00:00:43,934 --> 00:00:45,734
你的主意真的帮了大忙
Your idea really helped me out.

18
00:00:45,736 --> 00:00:48,370
我的光锥量子化论文已经上线了
My light-cone quantization paper's online already.

19
00:00:48,372 --> 00:00:50,873
反响非常热烈
The response has been amazing.

20
00:00:50,875 --> 00:00:52,307
真是太好了
Well, that's fascinating.

21
00:00:52,309 --> 00:00:53,776
我等不及拜读了
I can't wait to read it.

22
00:00:53,778 --> 00:00:55,110
哦 我也是
Oh, no, me as well.

23
00:00:55,112 --> 00:00:59,214
请发送到Sheldon@逗你玩 点 鄙之
Uh, please e-mail it to Sheldon@Bazinga.biz.

24
00:00:59,216 --> 00:01:00,549
为什么用"点 鄙之"?
Why "dot-biz"?

25
00:01:00,551 --> 00:01:02,084
因为我刚鄙视你了
Because I just gave you the business.

26
00:01:03,253 --> 00:01:05,254
{\an8}(.com其实是常用域名后缀 为和前面笑点统一 此处没有直译)

27
00:01:03,253 --> 00:01:05,254
而且 逗你玩 点 康姆 被人注册掉了
And also Bazinga.com was taken.

28
00:01:06,923 --> 00:01:08,924
再次感谢你
Anyway, thanks again.

29
00:01:08,926 --> 00:01:10,592
Cooper 滚蛋去
Cooper, suck eggs.

30
00:01:13,096 --> 00:01:15,330
你什么时候开始帮Barry Kripke了?
Since when do you help out Barry Kripke?

31
00:01:15,332 --> 00:01:17,833
我一直试图从细胞自动机的角度研究
Well, I'd been thinking about a cellular automata approach

32
00:01:17,835 --> 00:01:19,334
神经元连通性
to neuronal connectivity,

33
00:01:19,336 --> 00:01:21,170
我觉得它在弦理论领域可能会有一些
and I thought it might have some interesting applications

34
00:01:21,172 --> 00:01:22,738
有趣的应用... 没什么大不了的
to string theory... it's not a big deal.

35
00:01:22,740 --> 00:01:24,640
真的吗?
Oh, really?

36
00:01:24,642 --> 00:01:27,309
当我研究弦理论碰壁的时候
When I was doing string theory and hit a dead end,

37
00:01:27,311 --> 00:01:29,077
你为什么没试着帮我?
why didn't you try to help me?

38
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:32,080
我想帮你的... 但你说生物学家唯一会做的算数
I did ... you said the only math biologists know is

39
00:01:32,082 --> 00:01:34,249
就是如果你有三只青蛙 一只跳走了
if you have three frogs and one hops away,

40
00:01:34,251 --> 00:01:36,485
那就只剩两只青蛙了
that leaves two frogs.

41
00:01:36,487 --> 00:01:39,755
真有趣 听着的确像我说的
That's pretty funny, that does sound like me.

42
00:01:39,757 --> 00:01:40,923
但这并不意味着
But that doesn't mean

43
00:01:40,925 --> 00:01:42,891
你就应该站在街角
that you should be standing on street corners

44
00:01:42,893 --> 00:01:46,128
把你的数学理论送给路过的陌生人
handing out your math to whatever guy comes along.

45
00:01:47,497 --> 00:01:49,164
Sheldon 我们都是科学家
Sheldon, we're all scientists.

46
00:01:49,166 --> 00:01:50,833
我帮了一个同事
I helped out a fellow colleague.

47
00:01:50,835 --> 00:01:52,167
你太小气了
You're being petty.

48
00:01:52,169 --> 00:01:53,769
我小气?
I'm being petty?

49
00:01:53,771 --> 00:01:57,105
你明知道我和Barry在研究上是竞争关系
You know Barry and I have a professional rivalry.

50
00:01:57,107 --> 00:01:59,208
你也听到他说的了... 他让我滚蛋
You heard him... he told me to suck eggs.

51
00:01:59,210 --> 00:02:01,210
如果我们是朋友 他就会让我去
If we were friends, he would have suggested

52
00:02:01,212 --> 00:02:02,611
滚点好东西
I suck something more pleasant.

53
00:02:05,782 --> 00:02:07,482
你干嘛笑?
Why are you laughing?

54
00:02:07,484 --> 00:02:08,984
你学到什么了吗?
Did you learn something?

55
